How to compile this program:
run:
	make
How to run this program:
	./rt <input.iv> <output.ppm> <yres> <xres> <shadow_on> <reflection_on>
        You can also run the script:
                ./script_stdsun.sh
        It will generate the sphere3s_reflection.ppm, mickeyspheres_reflection.ppm, sphereCycloidLit_reflection.ppm, sphereCycloid_reflection.ppm and sphereTowerLit_reflection.ppm as xres 500, yres 500 1 1

